('IRONMAN 70.3 Leipzig', ARRAY['IRONMAN 70.3', 'IRONMAN 70.3 Leipzig Leipzig', 'IRONMAN 70.3 Leipzig Germany'], 'tri', 'triathlon', '70.3 / Half Ironman', 113, '', 'Leipzig', '', 'Germany', '', NULL, NULL, '', 2026, '2026-08-23', NULL, 8, 23, 'ironman', 'https://www.ironman.com/races/im703-leipzig', 'https://www.ironman.com/races/im703-leipzig', 14, 'IRONMAN 70.3', 'General Registration Sold Out', 'Lake', 'Flat', 'Flat', 25, 14, 22, NULL, NULL, 'source-page', 'Dive into the vibrant energy of Leipzig, where history meets creativity and every corner tells a story. Start with an easy out-and-back swim in the calm waters of Cospudener Lake, bike through stunning landscapes as you pass the beautiful lake district before returning to the buzz of the city center and finish in front of the Red Bull Arena.', 'Road / Open Water', 'Rolling', 100, '2026-03-28T14:05:41.733Z'),
('IRONMAN 70.3 Tallinn', ARRAY['IRONMAN 70.3', 'IRONMAN 70.3 Tallinn Tallinn', 'IRONMAN 70.3 Tallinn Estonia'], 'tri', 'triathlon', '70.3 / Half Ironman', 113, '', 'Tallinn', '', 'Estonia', '', NULL, NULL, '', 2026, '2026-08-23', NULL, 8, 23, 'ironman', 'https://www.ironman.com/races/im703-tallinn', 'https://www.ironman.com/races/im703-tallinn', 14, 'IRONMAN 70.3', 'Registration Now Open', 'Bay', 'Flat', 'Flat', 19, 10, 18, NULL, NULL, 'source-page', 'Race IRONMAN 70.3 Tallinn with a bay swim, flat bike and run courses in Estonia’s capital. Enjoy a fast race with scenic city views and mild summer weather!', 'Road / Open Water', 'Rolling', 100, '2026-03-28T14:05:41.733Z'),
